What you need to know:

The 2021 ARC calendar will have six rounds spread across the African continent. Rwanda will open the ARC calendar in March while South Africa will close the series in November.The complete 2021 ARC Calendar: Rwanda 20-21 March, Kenya 24-25 April, Tanzania 24-25 July, Uganda 21-22 August, Zambia 25-26 September, South Africa 6-7 November.